result.name: Dumpling Pro

reviews.text: Great little dumpling restaurant with a decent selection of dumplings and other dishes to choose from. Though perhaps not the best dumplings around, they were good and make a good meal if you're passing by. For English speakers like me; this seems to be a completely local restaurant and has an English menu and the staff speak enough of the language to help you get by.
Their pan fried dumplings are great. Try with the beef soup
Amazing dumpings and noodles, easy to find from MTR Jordan station. Each dumpling was juicy and filled to the brim!
Pretty good. Meat fried dumpligs.
Pak Choi pork dumpling with beef soup , dumpling is big and skin is soft 👍 soup is tasty too with few piece of beef brisket.

result.name: 龍鳳祥餃子館

reviews.text: 不錯👍
餃子🥟是現包的很好吃，又大顆！麵普通..但牛肉燉的入口即化！喜歡吃牛肉的可以嘗試！最後豆漿！必點太好喝啦！豆漿萬歲萬歲！不會太甜很濃的豆漿又便宜，我喝個精光❤️

感覺落左好多味精
比較好味是牛犇湯底，面也較彈牙
番茄湯底好似落左好多生粉咁
京蒽牛肉好生，又或者係好多防腐劑
餃子不過不失，可以再試，口水雞辣味夠但肉冰了點影響口感，服務有禮貌

蕃茄蛋幼麵配原味湯，味道正常。
是次人均消費約HK$50.
